_sText:
Please leave Any Feedback as it is very helpful!

Made completely by Samuel Webb.

Just extract the RAR to your counter strike source maps folder.

This fun and good looking map is gungame/ deathmatch (gg, dm) map so there are no buyzones.

It features pipes that act like teleports to one another, similar to what is seen in many Mario games.

There are 20 spawns for both CT/ T

Please comment  with constructive feedback and  yell out if there are any bugs/ exploits etc..
All feedback greatly appreciated.

Make time : A few days
Compile time: 10 mins
